title: Nuri Abdokov
text:
Nuri Edikovich Abdokov (; born 16 July 2000) is a Russian <a href="association%20football">football</a> player who plays for <a href="FC%20Kuban%20Krasnodar%20%282018%29">FC Kuban Krasnodar</a>.
Club career.
He made his debut in the <a href="Russian%20Football%20National%20League">Russian Football National League</a> for <a href="FC%20Kuban%20Krasnodar%20%282018%29">FC Kuban Krasnodar</a> on 10 July 2021 in a game against <a href="FC%20Torpedo%20Moscow">FC Torpedo Moscow</a>.
